org.batfish.dataplane.rib

Class Rib

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.dataplane.rib.AbstractRib<AbstractRoute>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, GenericRib<AbstractRoute>

    public class Rib
extends AbstractRib<AbstractRoute>
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a general RIB, capable of storing routes across different protocols. Uses administrative cost (a.k.a admin distance) to determine route preference.
